        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "No, Base64 is NOT encryption. It's just encoding for data transmission. Anyone can decode Base64. Use encryption for security."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Is this Base64 tool free?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Yes! 100% free, no signup required, unlimited conversions. All processing happens locally in your browser."
      }
    }
